data.description: Excellent home in a fantastic neighborhood with a prime location close to everything you could need!  Move right in to this three bedroom two full bathroom house with just over 1,500 square feet.  Two-car garage provides additional storage space with an extra bump-out perfect for your mower, tools, and toys!  Freshly painted wood on the fenced-in backyard provides an ideal place for kids or pets to play safely.  Cozy up with the living room gas fireplace perfect for these upcoming cold winter evenings.  Newer furnace!  Newer water heater!  This is a great home in an unbeatable location just minutes from everything you could need at Chapel Ridge along with quick access to 469!  Schedule your showing today!
